competitive_positioning.differentiation: Automated code generation from design systems for any coding stack.
competitive_vulnerabilities: Complexity of supporting all coding stacks

growth_bottlenecks: Integration complexity with various design tools
Educating the market on the benefits of design-to-code automation

key_risks: Maintaining compatibility with evolving design tools

strengths: Addresses a clear pain point in design-developer collaboration
Potential to significantly accelerate product development
concerns: Market education required for design-to-code automation

next_steps: Focus on key design tool integrations
Build a strong community of developers and designers
expansion_opportunities: Expand support for more coding stacks
Develop enterprise features for larger organizations
